description: This fine truck is serving San Jose unbelievably tasty Bar B. Q. and Southern comfort food, all homemade and full of flavor. You’ll find all your favorite comfort classics like Hot Link Sandwiches, Southern Fried Catfish, Pork Ribs, and of course all the best sides; Mac & Cheese, Red Beans & Rice, Potato Salad, and much more. Come on by H. Butler Bar.  Q for some majorly delicious grub that’s sure to make you “smile from the belly up”!
name: H. Butler's Bar B. Q.
